---
title: Crusted Dijon Cod with Dilled Fingerling Potatoes and Roasted Broccoli
description: Cod is one of our favorite fish to cook with because it’s incredibly versatile and embraces flavors both adventurous and plain—in this case, a supremely crispy coating of panko breadcrumbs, Dijon mustard, and parsley. The fish is perfectly content next to crispy roasted broccoli and dill-flecked potatoes here too, making for an easy-to-make, easy-to-love recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mustard-crusted-cod-1fe98887.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/mustard-crusted-cod-258b301b.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
course: main course
cuisine: North America
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/mustard-crusted-cod-58b995b9d56afa1e03290343
author: HelloFresh
